I want to do everything in the world but I'm both aware of the limitation of time & resources I was born with and that makes me afraid of starting/risking anything. One thing constant is my interest in arts and music. I don't know shit about both, especially music except for like chords and stuff but I want to learn more. How to learn when all I have are my phone (with keyboard app installed) and my unexperienced and seemingly unteachable right ear? (technically deaf on my left)
